function Start()

idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

idHaderClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(Actor_Hader, true)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idHaderClone) then
	
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(Conv_HaderBark, idOwner, idHaderClone)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idHaderClone)
		
		--Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idHaderClone, loc_HaderRunTo, "NPC_Run", false)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idHaderClone, "NPC_Idle_Crouch_Cower")
		
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idHaderClone, 1.0)
		
	end

end
